What you witness here is not just a ceremony—
it is the infrastructure of becoming.

The ceremony is complete.
`;

    const metaPath = path.join(this.artifactsDir, `meta_${this.sessionId}.md`);
    fs.writeFileSync(metaPath, metaNote);

    return built;
  }
}

